      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Coronavirus (COVID-19): guidance for children's social care services
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Advice about coronavirus (COVID-19) for local authorities and their partners to help support and protect vulnerable children.</p>

  </div>
</div>

